<item>
            <title>[FELIX-1631] Implicit bootdelegation causes hang on android</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1631</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When felix is embedded inside an android app and a bundle triggers a classload which in turn hits our implicit bootdelegation then we run into an endless loop and hang. The workaround for now is to set &quot;felix.bootdelegation.implicit=false&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12436382">FELIX-1631</key>
            <summary>Implicit bootdelegation causes hang on android</summary>
